verbose_text: We further found that the activation of eNOS induced by 17-beta-estradiol (E2) or the GPR30 agonist, G1, was inhibited by an inhibitor of PI3K / Akt (wortmannin), suggesting the activation of eNOS induced by 17-beta-estradiol (E2) is Akt dependent in endothelial cells under H/R conditions.
